# Task 2 – Responsive Design using Flexbox & CSS Grid

## Overview
A fully responsive webpage built using CSS Flexbox and CSS Grid with media queries.

## Features
- Flexbox navbar (collapses on mobile)
- CSS Grid 3-column card layout (2-col tablet, 1-col mobile)
- Grid-based sidebar + content layout
- Media queries at 768px and 480px breakpoints
- Mobile-first responsive design

## Tools Used
- HTML5, CSS3
- VS Code, Chrome DevTools

## How to Run
Open `index.html` in any browser.